### 1. REGISTRAR ADMINISTRADOR (Control total)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nombre": "rafa12",
    "email": "rafa@refaccionaria.com",
    "password": "admin123",
    "role": "administrador"
}

###

### 2. REGISTRAR VENDEDOR (Pantalla de ventas)
